article.description: — Tre Mitchell had 31 points and 11 rebounds as UMass beat Northeastern 94-79 on Friday.
article.headline: Mitchell scores 31 to lead UMass past Northeastern 94-79
article.linkText: Mitchell scores 31 to lead UMass past Northeastern 94-79
article.story: AMHERST, Mass. -- — Tre Mitchell had 31 points and 11 rebounds as UMass beat Northeastern 94-79 on Friday. Javohn Garcia had 23 points for UMass (1-0). Carl Pierre added 14 points. T.J. Weeks had 11 points. Tyson Walker had 29 points and five steals for the Huskies (0-1). Jahmyl Telfort added 13 points. Jason Strong had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
